rea": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/21854971"}}, "attached_info": "CjwIpvXkj/bc3qZnEAMaBjkyMjg2MCD+kJKTBTAAOOwjQA9yCDIxODU0OTcxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1778834963.226054", "card_id": "Q_2038219236431098730", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 286}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男子应聘程序员被要求先养两个月猪，HR 称工作成果需落地养殖场，要在前期接触养殖业务，这种要求合理吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，牧原食品股份有限公司入职要求引发网友热议。有网友吐槽，应聘程序员岗位时，被要求先到牧场养两个月猪，人事称是为了掌握养猪技能、熟悉厂区环境。 对此，牧原 HR 回应称，因程序员研发等岗位工作成果需落地养殖场，员工需深入了解主营业务，基本上所有岗位都需要在入职前期去接触养殖业务，各部门养殖时间也有所不同。 来源：潇湘晨报"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-26c57ea9faee9d1e75f0965cf6469455_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "167 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038219236431098730"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIpvXkj/bc3qZnEAMaCTExOTUwMjY3NSD2gpXQBjAAON8CQBByEzIwMzgyMTkyMzY0MzEwOTg3MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1778834963.226745", "card_id": "Q_2037133010990884347", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "追觅 CEO 俞浩一天狂发 75 条视频，他是要开始做自媒体了吗？这是什么策略？对营销传播来说有效吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 11 日发布多条⬇️ 此前单日 75 条⬇️"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-2a391ccf5cea7b96eafda536ae05f5dc_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "137 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037133010990884347"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIpvXkj/bc3qZnEAMaCTExOTQ2Mjg3OSDVm4XQBjAAOEJAEXITMjAzNzEzMzAxMDk5MDg4NDM0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1778834963.227438", "card_id": "Q_2035429478663444199", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 60}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "药店「闭店潮」持续，一年净减 2.2 万家，中小药店加快被淘汰出局，为啥会这样？对普通人买药影响大吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "药店行业从 2024 年第四季度出现的闭店潮还在持续，根据中康数据，2025 年全国药店净减少 2.2 万家。 药店行业在洗牌过程中呈现两级分化趋势，中小药店加快被淘汰出局，而龙头连锁药店靠着运营效率提升，利润正在得到修复。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ee792db9d075e556da4baf5080156c48.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "112 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2035429478663444199"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIpvXkj/bc3qZnEAMaCTExOTQwNTEyMyDMtuzPBjAAOLwBQBJyEzIwMzU0Mjk0Nzg2NjM0NDQxOTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1778834963.228135", "card_id": "Q_2038012082130563099", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 96}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你怎么看待南京审计大学男生偷拍女生裙底光速开除学籍，而华南理工大学男生偷拍女生裙底仅留校察看？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 11 日华南理工大学一名男学生在教室内偷拍女同学裙底，事件引发网络热议。对此，华南理工大学党委宣传部回应，事件发生后学校第一时间介入核查处置，目前已依规对涉事男生作出留校察看处分，涉事双方也已经协商沟通，达成和解共识。校方补充表示，事件发生后，各学院老师都已着手安抚学生情绪，后续还将加强全校学生法制教育与心理健康疏导工作。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-19cd17861813522d6d1e4f65b976db69_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "112 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038012082130563099"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIpvXkj/bc3qZnEAMaCTExOTQ5NjI5MiCIgZLQBjAAOKIBQBNyEzIwMzgwMTIwODIxMzA1NjMwOTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1778834963.228728", "card_id": "Q_2032583875399001561", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "贾跃亭为什么总能融到钱？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com